      "comment": "COMANCHE CHIEF (7) had a tough draw to overcome and was game in defeat when only 0.8 lengths from Mackenzie Rose in third (25.12) at this track. Makes plenty of appeal. VIENNA STORM (4) recorded his best time this course and distance latest, finishing a 3.5 lengths third behind Problem Solver in 25.02. Strong run latest and looks a key chance on that form. AMARYLLIS (2) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fifth (23.75) in a Bottom Up - Restricted Win at Warragul. Likely to be about the money. DR. EMILIA (5) should bounce back after an unplaced effort here recently. Something for the Multiples: TAKE A PANTHER (8)",
